Challenge Topics

format_topics.Rd

Challenge Topics

topic_tags

format_topics(params)

Arguments

params

Challenge parameters as list.

Format

topic_tags is a character vector of valid topic tags.

Value

format_topics() returns a character value indicating the challenge topic tags.
